{
  "openapi": "3.1.0",
  "info": {
    "title": "Crypto GPT Aggregator API",
    "description": "A minimal aggregation layer for Custom GPT Actions. It wraps selected free or free-tier crypto, macro, regulatory, and on-chain data sources behind a smaller set of GPT-friendly endpoints.\n\nAuthentication: configure Custom GPT Actions to send `X-API-Key: <your token>`.\nA Bearer token in the `Authorization` header is also accepted for manual testing.",
